<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-include path="../partials/head-attributes.mjml" />
    <mj-include path="../partials/responsive-styles.mjml" />

</mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#F9FAFB">
    <mj-include path="../partials/header.mjml" />

    <mj-section padding="24px 24px 0 24px" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 8px 0">Hi {{dealer.firstName}} 👋,</mj-text>

        <mj-text>
          You're invited to join CarExpert Exchange, the new platform built to connect you directly with ready-to-buy customers from CarExpert.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="12px 0 0 0">
          By activating your account, you'll:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="4px 0 0 0">✔️ Receive qualified new-car enquiries, not cold leads</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="4px 0 0 0">✔️ Quote quickly and manage all offers in one place</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="4px 0 0 0">✔️ Pay only when a sale is made - no wasted spend</mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="12px 0 0 0">
          Click below to activate your account for free and start quoting:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-button href="{{deal.url}}" align="center" font-size="18px" padding="16px 0 0 0">
          Activate my account
        </mj-button>

        <mj-text padding="8px 0 0" font-size="12px" line-height="16px" color="#6b7280" align="center">
          Can't click the button?
          <a href="{{deal.url}}" style="color:#6b7280; text-decoration:underline;">Open the invitation</a>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#E5E7EB" padding="16px 0" />

        <mj-text padding="0 0 0 0">
          <strong>Tip:</strong> Bookmark <a href="https://exchange.carexpert.com.au" color="#000000" text-decoration="underline">exchange.carexpert.com.au</a> ⭐ so it's always easy to find, and add this email address to your contacts so you never miss a deal.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#E5E7EB" padding="16px 0" />


        <mj-text>
          Once activated, you'll get email alerts each time a new deal is available. Simply log in, review the enquiry, and submit your best offer.
        </mj-text>

            <mj-text padding="16px 0 0 0">We're excited to have you on board.</mj-text>
 <mj-include path="../partials/sign-off.mjml" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-include path="../partials/footer.mjml" />
  </mj-body>
</mjml>

